headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Quanta Services (PWR) After Its Strong Multi Year Rally
summary: If you are wondering whether Quanta Services at around US$519 per share still offers value, the key is to look past the headline price and focus on what various valuation tools are saying. The stock has seen mixed recent moves, with a 0.9% decline over the last 7 days, an 11.3% gain across 30 days, an 18.1% return year to date, and a 78.0% return over the past year, on top of a very large 3 year and 5 year return profile.
